  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to determine the effect of suvorexant on insomnia symptoms in peri-
      and postmenopausal women who are experiencing sleep difficulties related to nighttime hot
      flashes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
